<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
    <title>로그인 - Forest Haven</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google Fonts & Icons -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <div class="login-wrapper p-4">
        <div class="login-container shadow-2xl border-0">
            <div class="row g-0 min-h-600">
                <!-- Brand Side (Hidden on Mobile) -->
                <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-md-flex login-brand-side">
                    <div class="navbar-brand">
                        <div class="brand-icon bg-white text-primary shadow-sm">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined fs-4">forest</span>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="brand-name text-white">Forest Haven</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="display-5 fw-black text-white mb-4">자연과 하나되는<br>특별한 휴식</h1>
                        <p class="text-white opacity-75 fs-5">포레스트 헤이븐에서 숲의 평온함을 느껴보세요.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Form Side -->
                <div class="col-md-6 p-4 p-lg-5 bg-white">
                    <!-- Mobile Logo -->
                    <div class="d-md-none mb-5 text-primary">
                        <div class="navbar-brand">
                            <div class="brand-icon shadow-sm"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">forest</span></div>
                            <h2 class="brand-name">Forest Haven</h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h3 fw-bold text-dark mb-2">환영합니다!</h2>
                        <p class="text-secondary small fw-medium">포레스트 헤이븐 계정으로 로그인하세요.</p>
                    </div>

                    <form class="mb-5">
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label class="form-label small fw-bold text-secondary">이메일 주소</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control py-3 shadow-none border-secondary border-opacity-25" placeholder="example@forest.com">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label class="form-label small fw-bold text-secondary">비밀번호</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control py-3 shadow-none border-secondary border-opacity-25" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요">
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
                            <div class="form-check">
                                <input class="form-check-input shadow-none" type="checkbox" id="rememberMe">
                                <label class="form-check-label small text-secondary" for="rememberMe">로그인 상태 유지</label>
                            </div>
                            <a href="#" class="text-primary small fw-bold text-decoration-none hover-underline">비밀번호를 잊으셨나요?</a>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100 py-3 fw-bold shadow-md border-0 mb-4 rounded-3">로그인</button>
                    </form>

                    <!-- Social Login -->
                    <div class="position-relative mb-5 text-center">
                        <hr class="text-secondary opacity-10">
                        <span class="position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle bg-white px-3 small text-secondary fw-bold divider-text">간편 로그인</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row g-3 mb-5">
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <button type="button" class="btn social-btn w-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                                <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBd5jFIvsJdNhbh5eAmdyjJ1gTSznmrTNbqlyu0SukckRwbulWEj4ZOMOt2pQGq0P268JoTWrlCbegI5Wl33XENJgRJopF94iWxhdHgXblurpR7TPalwy0tvpKW5JLwK-FxCLdnS7aPGPm9KFtMQPblxs9jR1y3OlK4djkWZ9mqve72GDpKq5UVwsu8ZVHwnDG--mQZLjC0MPf96r8VRk7IsNGQP2-kNYsWNM-f7k6eL8oldEnALJVZlH6ujnGn7j8RvexedqgyXKHP" alt="Kakao">
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <button type="button" class="btn social-btn w-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                                <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC3LYyThLTkj7suBdaEc-j5fnCq2Z7qDW53vS7cXbH7lTDnu0OTftgWE1OBItqisXqbf1VqHbuOWA5mAZydMIw0kM3djalxhPfXsWfXEmENKpxXtpcjgMh7gaGM9hF6ED6KVOFuJfcp3s4Wo-qtUscrkHGjik4RwWCCvOVVBk6b7NVrAUwkMmo6guQO3FfjnhkZoWA6Sc-0yYcsVjLzKoXJ872We5giS_3KfwIx8OXvhZ7kPo4MFtkHDJed8cPu4ywSkZ4u4TnCSP9z" alt="Naver">
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <button type="button" class="btn social-btn w-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                                <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCc7ULq8ZrrtpB3gcgoFUf6atZUjb0Gmsu-z5IOFIVqhjbyygrbjm1rzzDayiqUmReujDs11cZhedo9BK7ZL5lp9P_Sz6n2vsT472s-TegTJVltn27ZvSJ4YYamAE4h0FTz0ah0eA_RnMqS_rbdvhkDz8NohsddNYunW8fouuX0KOvJZHfcVc8qD8eqsDoWztfYnmLLDWSCdq0F8EIbg33xv1s6968nDDGuJ2qCWQsbTtjomCWgkMUEu_gOqo9Udi-mczWBc9UnEyHj" alt="Google">
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Bottom Links -->
                    <div class="text-center mt-auto">
                        <p class="small text-secondary mb-3">아직 회원이 아니신가요? <a href="/join-form" class="text-primary fw-bold text-decoration-none hover-underline ms-1">회원가입</a></p>
                        <a href="/" class="text-secondary opacity-50 small d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-1 text-decoration-none hover-primary">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined fs-6">arrow_back</span>
                            홈으로 돌아가기
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
